   from cropland fields across China, representing a range of climate and
   soil types. Mean soil BNE rate in croplands was estimated at 0.93 kg N
   ha(-1) yr(-1) and varied among the climatic zones, where the highest
   rate was in the north subtropical zone (1.66 kg N ha(-1) yr(-1)) and the
   lowest in the cold temperate zone (0.53 kg N ha(-1) yr(-1)). We
   estimated total national BNE for China based on the BNE rates for the
